<p><b>ā-gama- (BHS; BHSG, S. 210, s.v. gam [2] gama-ti)</b></p>  <p>“warten”#</p>  <p>⇒ ā-gamaya-, ā-game-</p><p>§ 4.13.5A6. atha khalu odanasampattir vvā āgamaṃtena bhuṃjitavyaṃ, vyañjana-sampattir vvā āgamaṃtena bhuñjitavyaṃ</p><p>§ 6.11.8A2. tena odanasampattī vā āgametavyaṃ vyañjanasampattī vā āgamaṃtena bhuñjitavyaṃ</p><p>§ 41.25.35B2. āgamitavyaṃ yāva tehi dhovitā pādā tti</p><p>§ 50.1.43A2. yāva paśyati so vihārakaṃ ghaṭṭitakaṃ. so dāni muhūrttakaṃ āgamiyāṇaṃ yadā nâgacchati, vihārakasya dvāramūle piṇḍapātakaṃ thapiya gato</p>
